The blue looks a little too dark in my opinion.

While the next lighter blue would look a little too bright. What do you think about using the same styles like for an active pagination list item:

I used
  background-color: ${theme.colors.variant.lightest.info};
  border-top: 1px solid ${theme.colors.variant.lighter.info};
  border-right: 1px solid ${theme.colors.variant.lighter.info};
  border-bottom: 1px solid ${theme.colors.variant.lighter.info};

for the title +
 background-color: ${isSelected ? theme.colors.variant.lighter.default : theme.colors.variant.lightest.info};
 border-bottom: 1px solid ${theme.colors.variant.lighter.info};
 border-left: 1px solid ${theme.colors.variant.lighter.info};

for Container -> IconWrapper -> ::after

